{"tid":842951,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋撚求助 好驚驚","createTime":"2018-09-30T17:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T09:04:58.000Z","uid":137188,"like":0,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a5103ebfb40ade9006024a32249889a96cdd5e1b","tid":842951,"uid":137188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"借account !<br />\n<br />\n話說我朋友早幾年同屋企關係唔好 諗住買私樓搬出去住 點知佢呀媽抑鬱發作 佢要照顧呀媽就好多時間留係公屋 掉空左層私樓 同時佢都同佢老豆講要除名 叫佢老豆搞<br />\n<br />\n去到2017年 房署有信要求報資產 佢先發現佢老豆無幫佢除名 係個陣佢呀媽個病都未好 加上掉空左係到就諗住賣樓 留番係公屋照顧老母 所以無報 怕比人收番間公屋 其實有埋私樓 佢地入息同埋資產都唔過<br />\n<br />\n到近期 收到房署信要求就私樓無報上去會面<br />\n<br />\n咁我朋友就好驚收番佢層公屋 因為私樓係2017 10月已經賣左 賣完個資產都唔過 同埋驚比房署告<br />\n<br />\n大家有無咩睇法 我朋友可以點做？"},{"pid":"159799426a6087bfe05fa1baed0ee2ff03656e68","tid":842951,"uid":176118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"掉空左都要計應課租值收入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e07ece453a492eaed113566b99a584734a3e643","tid":842951,"uid":42817,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"你自首啦。<br />\n一開始又話你借account，到最後又問你朋友可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a63827162bebd7c61344a89065e3ba56634dd38","tid":842951,"uid":137188,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"2e07ece453a492eaed113566b99a584734a3e643","tid":842951,"uid":42817,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"你自首啦。<br />\n一開始又話你借account，到最後又問你朋友可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:46:03.000Z","msg":"Ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0979169f2c4ac300f4a2f2567bbff333e8b876f","tid":842951,"uid":137188,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"159799426a6087bfe05fa1baed0ee2ff03656e68","tid":842951,"uid":176118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20